{"tid":2011793,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"立法會需要「精武黨」 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-05-11T08:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T03:46:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71f0e5adb0b8a22c68f053de2716d8e7122a9c81","tid":2011793,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200511/20915740/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200511%2F20915740%2F&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2Bnycv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=a4007868\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200511%2F20915740%2F&h=48bdbdc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200511/20915740/</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會需要「精武黨」 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200511/large/1589096249_7cc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200511%2Flarge%2F1589096249_7cc8.jpg&h=8fcac612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《破壊之王》截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n2004至2023年為風水上的八運，配艮卦，八運特色不是「發」，是不動如山、故步自封，所以老而不死、退而不休的losers老是常「出發」，不斷借屍還魂興風作浪。2024年九運來臨，特色是迅如烈火，舊模式舊思維舊價值一律冇得留低──這樣是好是壞，現在言之過早，只能說今天已入了八、九運過渡期，所以舊事物即使未被時代革掉，你也會覺得「變形走樣」篤眼篤鼻。立法會不就是這樣一種舊玩具嗎？<br />\n<br />\n去年7&middot;1佔領立法會，假如發生在200年前歐洲，政。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n市民不再認同這個政府、這個立法會。在現代文明社會，政府本質是公僕，鄭月娥是「妹仔」。大家。。。。。。。。。。。得，叫習近平恢復帝制先啦，那時候我們才慢慢跟你講三綱五常、君君臣臣。<br />\n<br />\n然而大眾記憶是短暫的──共產黨也深明此理──。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n切沒有發生。當然，作為和理非深深藍的我，是舉腳贊成「體制內抗爭」的（我去年六月已呼籲義士。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上週五，除了只看CCTVB新聞的人外，全香港都看。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n導致陳議員椎間盤移位。警方至今未有拘捕郭偉強。即使真的拘捕了檢控了，也難保不會由法官郭。。。。。。。。。。。有新思維，對議員也要有新要求。<br />\n<br />\n新一屆立法會不管是否「35+」，我理想中的非建制派黃金比例是「。文。武」：7成武藝高強，俠骨柔情，。成能言善辯，知書識法。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n堯用自拍神器襲擊陳志全，勇武議員就可擋在前面，先受他一棍，然後在電光火石間把他一腳踢飛三尺。警方可控訴兩人毆鬥，不妨雙雙DQ。<br />\n<br />\n很可惜，至今我還沒見到「精武黨」候選人。 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"13ff9bcff5278698d2d712008b3c48d983c9585d","tid":2011793,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭再出發<br />\n香港要獨立</span><br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴冒生命危險寄語香港人<br />\n街頭 議會 國際 三線<span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQXeSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQXeSo.png&h=c52485db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c784c77c696875e4e9457c6114faf64a16196d0","tid":2011793,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"30956d3c34a6a0939e4f4674bb1130760007d88a","tid":2011793,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:00:32.000Z","msg":"糧油+獨派走先港人4年"},{"pid":"0af8d896cc52802b9892a17a04117b0d392ce1e4","tid":2011793,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13ff9bcff5278698d2d712008b3c48d983c9585d","tid":2011793,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭再出發<br />\n香港要獨立</span><br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴冒生命危險寄語香港人<br />\n街頭 議會 國際 三線<span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQXeSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQXeSo.png&h=c52485db&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:46:54.000Z","msg":"樓價唔跌，即是封關對香港經濟沒有影響。 不如永久封關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2011325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2011325</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人工資10年間跌左一半 (以樓市購買力計算)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fssOdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fssOdS</a>"}]}